  "detailed_description": "Save Dash is a simple yet challenging hardcore running arcade game.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nAll you need to do is to jump through 18 different sectors and save a small creature called Dash.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nGame features:<br />\r\n* Stunning graphic<br />\r\n* Blood or no blood option<br />\r\n* 18 unique sectors<br />\r\n* 3 difficulty levels: Normal, Hard and Insane<br />\r\n* 11 different ways how Dash can die<br />\r\n<br />\r\nand more will come…<br />\r\n<br />\r\n10ravens team",
  "about_the_game": "Save Dash is a simple yet challenging hardcore running arcade game.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nAll you need to do is to jump through 18 different sectors and save a small creature called Dash.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nGame features:<br />\r\n* Stunning graphic<br />\r\n* Blood or no blood option<br />\r\n* 18 unique sectors<br />\r\n* 3 difficulty levels: Normal, Hard and Insane<br />\r\n* 11 different ways how Dash can die<br />\r\n<br />\r\nand more will come…<br />\r\n<br />\r\n10ravens team",
